{"tid":1890867,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓記憶體大廠SK海力士 隔離800名員工","createTime":"2020-02-21T11:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T12:04:00.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dcba16cfb8187e2a016d13bb41396941b18c0d63","tid":1890867,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎疫情席捲全球，南韓記憶體大廠「SK海力士」（SK hynix）驚傳有新進員工和武漢肺炎疑似患者曾有密切接觸，且該名新進員工有出現肺炎跡象，SK海力士週四（20日）表示，已對800名員工進行隔離。強調整起事件不影響公司運營。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》報導，SK海力士表示，該名新進員工位於首爾以南約70公里的利川廠，公司發現，該名員工曾和大邱武漢肺炎疑似患者有密切接觸。目前該廠區約800名員工已進行隔離。<br />\n<br />\nSK海力士表示，該名新進員工已送醫檢測，並在週三關閉了教育訓練中心，並把當時曾參與教育訓練的280名員工進行居家隔離。<br />\n<br />\nSK海力士利川廠共有1.8萬名員工，強調整起事件不影響公司運營。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3074030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3074030&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVEBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=48a903d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3074030&h=078a31b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3074030</a>"},{"pid":"ec6eb6cf4c3ead9ef86942aa39d2f153d9b6dcb3","tid":1890867,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"支那害全世界"},{"pid":"750d2ef2169fd7c5a64dd5cef1912e23631f681a","tid":1890867,"uid":219256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}